title: SET_ROUTING_BUCKET_ENTITY_LOCKDOWN_MODE
content:
0xA0F2201F// SetRoutingBucketEntityLockdownMode
void SET_ROUTING_BUCKET_ENTITY_LOCKDOWN_MODE(int bucketId, char* mode);Parameters:bucketId: The routing bucket ID to adjust.mode: One of aforementioned modes.Sets the entity lockdown mode for a specific routing bucket.Lockdown modes are:ModeMeaningstrictNo entities can be created by clients at all.relaxedOnly script-owned entities created by clients are blocked.inactiveClients can create any entity they want.
